en:
The C.R.O.QU.AN is a climbing club open all year for beginners to advanced climbers - individuals, families and groups (schools, leisure centres, businesses, birthday parties, stag/hen parties, etc.) and to all disabled visitors.
Each session generally lasts around 1 hour 30 minutes.
Equipped with the best boulder areas (climbing without ropes) in Calvados, the club is of particular interest.
We also propose courses during school holidays.
